{
  "texts": [
    "Sequence duplicates were removed using CD-HIT 77 at an identity threshold of 80%, and 80% and 20% were randomly sorted into a 'training' and a 'test' set, respectively.",
    "A training MSA was generated by an iterative process using MUSCLE (v3.8) 78.",
    "Round 1 MDH.",
    "All UniProt sequences containing an Ldh_1_N Pfam domain followed by an Ldh_1_C domain were downloaded.",
    "LDH and MDH enzymes, based on enzyme commission number 79, 1.1.1.27 for LDH and 1.1.1.37 for MDH, were downloaded from SwissProt."
  ]
}